    Get Bollinger bands Calculates upper and lower Bollinger bands based on standard deviation of stock's close prirce over the past 20 days

    get_bbands.Rd

    Get Bollinger bands Calculates upper and lower Bollinger bands based on standard deviation of stock's close prirce over the past 20 days

    Usage

    get_bbands(stock_ticker)

    Arguments

    stock_ticker

    String. Stock ticker of company to be analysed such as "MSFT"

    Value

    tibble containing upper and lower Bollinger bands adjusted closing price, moving average, date

    Examples

    get_bbands("MSFT")
